        {
          "text": "Lei Liang —",
          "textSize": "heading-two"
        },
        {
          "text": "Six Seasons ",
          "italic": true,
          "textSize": "heading-two"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "Chinese-born, U.S.-based composer whose work engages endangered soundscapes and intercultural listening practices. "
        },
        {
          "text": "Six Seasons ",
          "italic": true
        },
        {
          "text": "(2022) features hydrophone recordings of Arctic ice and marine life integrated with a string quartet, treating environmental sound as an ensemble member rather than a backdrop. “Season” here is defined by environmental change rather than calendar time. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
